A Parallel Discrete Event Simulation (PDES) system implemented on a Convey HC-2ex coprocessor.

This project, at this moment,  implements a rudimentary form of the phold algorithm.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:
- To set up the environment:

    source /opt/convey/pdk2/<rev>/settings.(c)sh

- To compile the application:

    cd app
    make

- To run the simulation:

    cd /sim
    ./runsim

- To build the personality:

    cd phys
    make
